45:05.081 --> 45:06.738
Yeah, it'll be good.

45:06.773 --> 45:08.050
They run a traveling kitchen

45:08.084 --> 45:09.534
that brings local ingredients,

45:09.568 --> 45:11.122
Appalachian recipes,

45:11.156 --> 45:13.952
